## 3. Sequence Diagrams (Mermaid)

{% for flow in sequence_flows %}
### {{ flow.title }}

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User
    participant System as System
    {% if flow.actors %}
    {% for actor in flow.actors.split(',') %}
    {% set a = actor.strip() %}
    {% if a|lower not in ['user', 'system'] %}
    participant {{ a.replace(' ', '_') }} as {{ a }}
    {% endif %}
    {% endfor %}
    {% endif %}

    {% if flow.steps %}
    {% for line in flow.steps.strip().split('\n') %}
    {% set line = line.strip() %}
    {% if line %}
    {% if '->' in line %}
    {% set parts = line.split('->') %}
    {% set from_to = parts[0].strip().split(':') %}
    {% set from = from_to[0].strip() if from_to[0] else 'User' %}
    {% set to_parts = (parts[1] if parts|length > 1 else ':action').strip().split(':') %}
    {% set to = to_parts[0].strip() if to_parts[0] else 'System' %}
    {% set action = to_parts[1].strip() if to_parts|length > 1 else 'action' %}
    {% if '-->>' in line %}
    {{ from }}-->>{{ to }}: {{ action }}
    {% else %}
    {{ from }}->>{{ to }}: {{ action }}
    {% endif %}
    {% else %}
    Note over User,System: {{ line }}
    {% endif %}
    {% endif %}
    {% endfor %}
    {% endif %}
```

{% else %}
_No sequence flows defined._

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User
    participant System as System
    User->>System: Action
    System-->>User: Response
```

